`}</pre>
          </div>
          <p class="text-parchment-600 max-w-lg text-lg leading-snug">
            UI Skills is a collection of design-engineering skills to help
            humans and agents create better interfaces.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-parchment-200/40 rounded-[12px] p-4 sm:p-5">
          <h2 class="text-parchment-900 text-base font-medium text-balance">
            How to use
          </h2>
          <p
            class="text-parchment-600 mt-3 max-w-2xl text-base leading-snug text-pretty"
          >
            Ask your agent to run the CLI first so it can choose the right skill
            before making changes.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center">
            <CodeBlock
              className="w-full max-w-2xl"
              align="center"
              mobileSurface
              wrapOnMobile
              lines={[
                [
                  {
                    text: "Run `npx ui-skills start` to fix this dialog motion.",
                  },
                ],
              ]}
              copyContent="Run `npx ui-skills start` to fix this dialog motion."
            />
          </div>

          <p
            class="text-parchment-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-snug text-pretty"
          >
            Or browse the collection below to find the best design-engineering
            skills.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="px-4 sm:px-0">
          <h2 class="text-parchment-900 text-base font-medium text-balance">
            Collection
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-3 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
            {
              displayedSkills.map((skill) => (
                <SkillCard
                  href={`/skills/${skill.pathSlug}`}
                  slug={skill.slug}
                  description={skill.description}
                  ownerLabel={skill.ownerLabel}
                  avatarUrl={skill.avatarUrl}
                />
              ))
            }
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center px-4 sm:px-0">
            <Button href="/skills"> See all skills </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
